 \left(1 + \frac{r}{n}\right)^n = \sum_{i = 0}^n \binom{n}{i} \left(\frac{r}{n}\right)^i = \sum_{i = 0}^n \frac{n!}{i!(n - i)!} \cdot \frac{r^i}{n^i} \\ = \sum_{i = 0}^n \frac{r^i}{i!} \left(\frac{n(n - 1) \dotsb (n - i + 1)}{n^i}\right) \leq \sum_{i = 0}^n \frac{r^i}{i!}. 
